snippet.title: Mandi Balon Ajaib ❤ Unboxing Magic Water Balloons Challenge Toys Funny Video
snippet.description:
Mainan anak balon ajaib bisa isi 100 balon secara serentak dalam satu menit, hebatkan teman teman. Fill 100+ Balloons in under 1 Minute - Lifia Niala mandi waktu balon! Salah satu mainan paling lucu yang keluar tahun ini adalah sekelompok kecil balon air. Anak-anak berlarian melempar balon air satu sama lain. Mereka berlari dan tertawa dengan hal kecil konyol ini yang sangat sederhana dan tidak terstruktur.

Video lucu! Lifia Niala asik mandi balon ajaib yang bisa diisi cepat kurang dari 1 menit untuk 100 balon Kids Toy. 

Begitu banyak kehidupan anak-anak yang terstruktur sekarang karena waktu bermain mereka justru sebaliknya. Mereka mendambakan kebebasan itu.

Balon ajaib adalah must-have untuk semua keluarga. Dari pertarungan air sore spontan di barbekyu keluarga hingga pertarungan balon air besar di taman lokal - pastikan Anda dan teman Anda siap untuk diserang dengan kekuatan Balon Revo Magic yang Anda inginkan. Sistem ini tidak hanya akan membantu Anda mendominasi lawan Anda (mengisi 100 balon air dalam 1 menit), pikirkan semua kesenangan yang akan Anda hadapi dengan pertarungan balon air ini!

Fitur Produk :
Termasuk 3 Bundel Balon dan 3 Paket Isi Ulang. Sebanyak 220 Balon.
Cepat isi 100+ Balon di bawah 1 menit.
Mudah digunakan dan menyenangkan bagi seluruh keluarga.
Membuat tambahan yang bagus untuk pertemuan keluarga atau tamasya bisnis / organisasi.

snippet.title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit Playset Toys Unboxing
snippet.description:
We love Mickey Mouse and Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse! See all of our Surprise videos   http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLoLQ9unpi4OEEM3rUVjLGa0pUaXQvW3Wd

Please Subscribe Here http://www.youtube.com/user/TheEngineeringFamily?sub_confirmation=1

The Disney Junior Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit is a way for your Mickey Mouse Fan into a doctor. There are similar Disney Junior Doc McStuffins Doctor kits, but this one is definitely designed for a Mickey Mouse fan.

Notes-

- Comes with a battery operated stethoscope. The stethoscope is probably the highlight of the set.

- Has a thermometer for checking temperature - each time you click the thermometer you change the temperature on its display.

- A small flashlight is included for checking throats and ears

- The blood pressure cuff doesn't pump with air.... unlike the one that comes with the Doc mcStuffins playset

- Has a small mirror

- A few other items are included like two band aids

Final Verdict - Our daughter prefers the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor kit over-and-above the one from Doc McStuffins. She prefers the blood pressure cuff from Doc McStuffins but she likes all of the additional doctor tools in the Mickey kit.

4 1/2 Stars

snippet.title: PJ Masks Owlette Owl Glider Vehicle - Unboxing Demo Review Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Get ready for some super Owl wings! with the PJ Masks Owlette's Owl Glider vehicle!  It's fun to push along, and comes with a 3-inch fully articulated Gekko figure!  The Gekko-Mobile also has seats to fit all 3 PJ Masks heroes!     

Available at Amazon here:
Owlette's Owl-Glider: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Owlette-Flyer-Vehicle/dp/B01HXNDA6C/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

PJ Masks figures : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yW-ANqN-_VM

PJ Masks is about three 6-year-olds, Connor, Amaya, and Greg, who lead relatively normal lives by day, where they are neighbors, classmates, and friends. However, at night, they put on their pyjamas and become Catboy, Owlette, and Gekko, and fight crime as the superhero team PJ Masks. Together, they go on adventures, defeat villains, solve mysteries, and learn valuable lessons. Catboy has super-hearing using Cat Ears, can leap high and far using Super Cat Jump, and sprints fast using Super Cat Speed.  Gecko can use Super Gekko Camouflage to change colors and blend in with his surroundings, Super Gekko Muscles (aka Super Muscles) to lift heavy things, Super Lizard Grip to climb walls or anchor himself to stop vehicles, and Super Lizard Water Run to walk on water. Owlette is able to see in the dark using Owl Eyes (or Super Owl Eyes) and fly by using Super Owl Wings, which she can also use to launch gusts of air to send opponents flying backward,[8] which she calls her Owl Wing Wind.

=========================================

A toy review by Keith's Toy Box where you can enjoy kid-friendly videos for babies, infants, toddlers, pre-school and primary school children. Watch unboxing, exciting demos, in slow motion, and time lapse, and play with these tried and tested toys from Hot Wheels, Thomas, Chuggington, Mega Bloks, Lego, Duplo, to Takara, Tomy, Tomica, Plarail, Disney Toys, Pixar Disney Cars, and Sesame Street! Great toy reviews for toy collectors young and old alike.

snippet.title: Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing!!!
snippet.description:
Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing + Extra Anger Cup from Disney

Riley's hot-tempered side is on show with this Anger Deluxe Talking Doll. He's not happy, and he's happy to let you know it. Press his hand to hear 13 phrases, and see his red face light up, plus you can create your own memory ball.

Your tummy will be hot-tempered after sipping from Anger's hefty hot beverage mug. Keep your cool under control from the Inside Out.

Inside Out is a 2015 American 3D computer-animated comedy-drama film produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures. The film is set in the mind of a young girl, Riley Andersen, where five personified emotions—Joy, Sadness, Fear, Anger, and Disgust —try to lead her through life as she moves with her parents to a new city. 

Divertida-Mente é um desenho animado 3D produzido pela Pixar Animation Studios e pela Walt Disney Pictures. O filme é definido na cabeça de uma jovem garota, Riley, onde 5 emoções - Medo, Tristeza, Alegria, Nojinho, Raiva-. tentam levar a menina através de sua vida.

『インサイド・ヘッド』（Inside Out）は、2015年公開のアメリカ合衆国のコンピュータアニメーション3D映画。アメリカ合衆国では2015年6月19日、日本では2015年7月18日に公開された。

Here is what "Inside Out" is called in other languages:  玩轉腦朋友 , 玩转脑朋友 , Vice Versa , ALLES STEHT KOPF

Here's how Toys is called in other languages: juegos, juguetes, giocattoli, spielwaren, brinquedos, carrinhos, spielsachen, leker, spielzeug, jouets, speelgoed, 玩具,leksaker, खिलौने, игрушки, đồ chơi, oyuncaklar, zabawki, bréagáin, Παιχνίδια, トイズ, 장난감, ġugarelli, hračky, іграшки.

Please watch our other videos! Here is our most popular one:
FROZEN MAKEUP BEAUTY KIT FROZEN TOY Disney Princess Elsa Anna Olaf
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CT1Oiwcw3hk

Subscribe to our channel to see videos of the other talking "Inside Out" dolls:  Disgust, Sadness, Joy, and Fear.  Enjoy!!! :-)

Rusty Rivets is a Canadian CGI interactive animated television series produced by Arc Productions and Spin Master Entertainment for Treehouse TV and Nickelodeon Productions. Inspired by elements of the maker culture, it follows the adventures of a young inventor named Rusty and his team of customized robots. A boy named Rusty Rivets uses his knowledge of engineering to repurpose machine parts and create gadgets. He lives in the city of Sparkton Hills along with his friend Ruby Ramirez, a robotic tyrannosaurid named Botasaur, and a group of smaller robots known as the Bits. The show highlights a variety of concepts related to basic science and technology.

Rusty uses the recurring catch phrase "modify, customize, Rustify" when personalizing inventions. Ruby changes the last word to "Rubify" when she does the alterations.

snippet.title: Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky High Bridge Jump Fisher-Price -  Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
Watch Thomas complete his most breathtaking stunt yet in the Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky-High Bridge Jump from Fisher-Price. This Thomas & Friends train set breaks new ground by taking Thomas off the tracks and sending him soaring through the air, delivering speed, excitement, and motorized action like only TrackMaster train sets can! Inspired by the Thomas & Friends DVD, The Great Race, Sky-High Bridge Jump brings the movie to life with fast-paced, flying thrills. After a tall, spiral ascent with Harold the helicopter, Thomas speeds down a huge ramp and the velocity launches him into the air! Thomas soars for over two feet (0,6 meters) through the air before landing safely on the other side and continuing his journey. This one-of-a-kind Thomas & Friends train set also features a cargo hopper, waving flags, a barrel cargo piece, and removable Harold the helicopter.
- Complete Thomas & Friends train set includes motorized Thomas train, Harold the helicopter, cargo hopper, cargo piece, and full track layout with ramp and bridge jump
- Send Thomas under the bridge and up the spiral track
- When Thomas reaches the end of the track, Harold will lift him to the top of the ramp
- Thomas lands safely and continues his journey around the rails
- Tip the hopper to drop the barrel onto the tracks and Thomas will push it into the cargo area

Available at Amazon here:
https://www.amazon.co.uk/Thomas-Friends-TrackMaster-Sky-High-Bridge/dp/B01ASVDF2K/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

snippet.title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit Playset Toys Unboxing
snippet.description:
We love Mickey Mouse and Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse! See all of our Surprise videos   http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLoLQ9unpi4OEEM3rUVjLGa0pUaXQvW3Wd

Please Subscribe Here http://www.youtube.com/user/TheEngineeringFamily?sub_confirmation=1

The Disney Junior Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit is a way for your Mickey Mouse Fan into a doctor. There are similar Disney Junior Doc McStuffins Doctor kits, but this one is definitely designed for a Mickey Mouse fan.

Notes-

- Comes with a battery operated stethoscope. The stethoscope is probably the highlight of the set.

- Has a thermometer for checking temperature - each time you click the thermometer you change the temperature on its display.

- A small flashlight is included for checking throats and ears

- The blood pressure cuff doesn't pump with air.... unlike the one that comes with the Doc mcStuffins playset

- Has a small mirror

- A few other items are included like two band aids

Final Verdict - Our daughter prefers the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor kit over-and-above the one from Doc McStuffins. She prefers the blood pressure cuff from Doc McStuffins but she likes all of the additional doctor tools in the Mickey kit.

4 1/2 Stars

snippet.title: PJ Masks Owlette Owl Glider Vehicle - Unboxing Demo Review Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Get ready for some super Owl wings! with the PJ Masks Owlette's Owl Glider vehicle!  It's fun to push along, and comes with a 3-inch fully articulated Gekko figure!  The Gekko-Mobile also has seats to fit all 3 PJ Masks heroes!     

Available at Amazon here:
Owlette's Owl-Glider: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Owlette-Flyer-Vehicle/dp/B01HXNDA6C/?tag=thewanfulworo-20
Gekko's Gekko-Mobile: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Gekko-Mobile-Vehicle/dp/B01HXNDBH0/?tag=thewanfulworo-20
Catboy's Cat-Car: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Cat-Boy-Car/dp/B01HXND5XK/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

Click here for more PJ Masks toy videos:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK3Sm4uckS7MSkz-VC_mrEYl

PJ Masks figures : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yW-ANqN-_VM

PJ Masks is about three 6-year-olds, Connor, Amaya, and Greg, who lead relatively normal lives by day, where they are neighbors, classmates, and friends. However, at night, they put on their pyjamas and become Catboy, Owlette, and Gekko, and fight crime as the superhero team PJ Masks. Together, they go on adventures, defeat villains, solve mysteries, and learn valuable lessons. Catboy has super-hearing using Cat Ears, can leap high and far using Super Cat Jump, and sprints fast using Super Cat Speed.  Gecko can use Super Gekko Camouflage to change colors and blend in with his surroundings, Super Gekko Muscles (aka Super Muscles) to lift heavy things, Super Lizard Grip to climb walls or anchor himself to stop vehicles, and Super Lizard Water Run to walk on water. Owlette is able to see in the dark using Owl Eyes (or Super Owl Eyes) and fly by using Super Owl Wings, which she can also use to launch gusts of air to send opponents flying backward,[8] which she calls her Owl Wing Wind.

=========================================

A toy review by Keith's Toy Box where you can enjoy kid-friendly videos for babies, infants, toddlers, pre-school and primary school children. Watch unboxing, exciting demos, in slow motion, and time lapse, and play with these tried and tested toys from Hot Wheels, Thomas, Chuggington, Mega Bloks, Lego, Duplo, to Takara, Tomy, Tomica, Plarail, Disney Toys, Pixar Disney Cars, and Sesame Street! Great toy reviews for toy collectors young and old alike.

snippet.title: Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing!!!
snippet.description:
Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing + Extra Anger Cup from Disney

Riley's hot-tempered side is on show with this Anger Deluxe Talking Doll. He's not happy, and he's happy to let you know it. Press his hand to hear 13 phrases, and see his red face light up, plus you can create your own memory ball.

Your tummy will be hot-tempered after sipping from Anger's hefty hot beverage mug. Keep your cool under control from the Inside Out.

Inside Out is a 2015 American 3D computer-animated comedy-drama film produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures. The film is set in the mind of a young girl, Riley Andersen, where five personified emotions—Joy, Sadness, Fear, Anger, and Disgust —try to lead her through life as she moves with her parents to a new city. 

Divertida-Mente é um desenho animado 3D produzido pela Pixar Animation Studios e pela Walt Disney Pictures. O filme é definido na cabeça de uma jovem garota, Riley, onde 5 emoções - Medo, Tristeza, Alegria, Nojinho, Raiva-. tentam levar a menina através de sua vida.

『インサイド・ヘッド』（Inside Out）は、2015年公開のアメリカ合衆国のコンピュータアニメーション3D映画。アメリカ合衆国では2015年6月19日、日本では2015年7月18日に公開された。

Here is what "Inside Out" is called in other languages:  玩轉腦朋友 , 玩转脑朋友 , Vice Versa , ALLES STEHT KOPF

Here's how Toys is called in other languages: juegos, juguetes, giocattoli, spielwaren, brinquedos, carrinhos, spielsachen, leker, spielzeug, jouets, speelgoed, 玩具,leksaker, खिलौने, игрушки, đồ chơi, oyuncaklar, zabawki, bréagáin, Παιχνίδια, トイズ, 장난감, ġugarelli, hračky, іграшки.

Please watch our other videos! Here is our most popular one:

https://youtu.be/583gnDKKDE4


Rusty Rivets is a Canadian CGI interactive animated television series produced by Arc Productions and Spin Master Entertainment for Treehouse TV and Nickelodeon Productions. Inspired by elements of the maker culture, it follows the adventures of a young inventor named Rusty and his team of customized robots. A boy named Rusty Rivets uses his knowledge of engineering to repurpose machine parts and create gadgets. He lives in the city of Sparkton Hills along with his friend Ruby Ramirez, a robotic tyrannosaurid named Botasaur, and a group of smaller robots known as the Bits. The show highlights a variety of concepts related to basic science and technology.

Rusty uses the recurring catch phrase "modify, customize, Rustify" when personalizing inventions. Ruby changes the last word to "Rubify" when she does the alterations.

snippet.title: Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky High Bridge Jump Fisher-Price -  Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
Watch Thomas complete his most breathtaking stunt yet in the Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky-High Bridge Jump from Fisher-Price. This Thomas & Friends train set breaks new ground by taking Thomas off the tracks and sending him soaring through the air, delivering speed, excitement, and motorized action like only TrackMaster train sets can! Inspired by the Thomas & Friends DVD, The Great Race, Sky-High Bridge Jump brings the movie to life with fast-paced, flying thrills. After a tall, spiral ascent with Harold the helicopter, Thomas speeds down a huge ramp and the velocity launches him into the air! Thomas soars for over two feet (0,6 meters) through the air before landing safely on the other side and continuing his journey. This one-of-a-kind Thomas & Friends train set also features a cargo hopper, waving flags, a barrel cargo piece, and removable Harold the helicopter.
- Complete Thomas & Friends train set includes motorized Thomas train, Harold the helicopter, cargo hopper, cargo piece, and full track layout with ramp and bridge jump
- Send Thomas under the bridge and up the spiral track
- When Thomas reaches the end of the track, Harold will lift him to the top of the ramp
- Thomas lands safely and continues his journey around the rails
- Tip the hopper to drop the barrel onto the tracks and Thomas will push it into the cargo area

snippet.title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit Playset Toys Unboxing
snippet.description:
We love Mickey Mouse and Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse! See all of our Surprise videos   http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLoLQ9unpi4OEEM3rUVjLGa0pUaXQvW3Wd

Please Subscribe Here http://www.youtube.com/user/TheEngineeringFamily?sub_confirmation=1

The Disney Junior Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit is a way for your Mickey Mouse Fan into a doctor. There are similar Disney Junior Doc McStuffins Doctor kits, but this one is definitely designed for a Mickey Mouse fan.

Notes-

- Comes with a battery operated stethoscope. The stethoscope is probably the highlight of the set.

- Has a thermometer for checking temperature - each time you click the thermometer you change the temperature on its display.

- A small flashlight is included for checking throats and ears

- The blood pressure cuff doesn't pump with air.... unlike the one that comes with the Doc mcStuffins playset

- Has a small mirror

- A few other items are included like two band aids

Final Verdict - Our daughter prefers the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor kit over-and-above the one from Doc McStuffins. She prefers the blood pressure cuff from Doc McStuffins but she likes all of the additional doctor tools in the Mickey kit.

4 1/2 Stars

TheEngineeringFamily has loads of family friendly content

snippet.title: PJ Masks Owlette Owl Glider Vehicle - Unboxing Demo Review Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Get ready for some super Owl wings! with the PJ Masks Owlette's Owl Glider vehicle!  It's fun to push along, and comes with a 3-inch fully articulated Gekko figure!  The Gekko-Mobile also has seats to fit all 3 PJ Masks heroes!     

Available at Amazon here:
Owlette's Owl-Glider: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Owlette-Flyer-Vehicle/dp/B01HXNDA6C/?tag=thewanfulworo-20
Gekko's Gekko-Mobile: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Gekko-Mobile-Vehicle/dp/B01HXNDBH0/?tag=thewanfulworo-20
Catboy's Cat-Car: https://www.amazon.com/PJ-Masks-Cat-Boy-Car/dp/B01HXND5XK/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

Click here for more PJ Masks toy videos:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK3Sm4uckS7MSkz-VC_mrEYl

PJ Masks figures : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yW-ANqN-_VM

PJ Masks is about three 6-year-olds, Connor, Amaya, and Greg, who lead relatively normal lives by day, where they are neighbors, classmates, and friends. However, at night, they put on their pyjamas and become Catboy, Owlette, and Gekko, and fight crime as the superhero team PJ Masks. Together, they go on adventures, defeat villains, solve mysteries, and learn valuable lessons. Catboy has super-hearing using Cat Ears, can leap high and far using Super Cat Jump, and sprints fast using Super Cat Speed.  Gecko can use Super Gekko Camouflage to change colors and blend in with his surroundings, Super Gekko Muscles (aka Super Muscles) to lift heavy things, Super Lizard Grip to climb walls or anchor himself to stop vehicles, and Super Lizard Water Run to walk on water. Owlette is able to see in the dark using Owl Eyes (or Super Owl Eyes) and fly by using Super Owl Wings, which she can also use to launch gusts of air to send opponents flying backward,[8] which she calls her Owl Wing Wind.

=========================================

A toy review by Keith's Toy Box where you can enjoy kid-friendly videos for babies, infants, toddlers, pre-school and primary school children. Watch unboxing, exciting demos, in slow motion, and time lapse, and play with these tried and tested toys from Hot Wheels, Thomas, Chuggington, Mega Bloks, Lego, Duplo, to Takara, Tomy, Tomica, Plarail, Disney Toys, Pixar Disney Cars, and Sesame Street! Great toy reviews for toy collectors young and old alike.

snippet.title: Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing!!!
snippet.description:
Disney / Pixar Inside Out Anger Talking Action Figure Toy Unboxing + Extra Anger Cup from Disney

Riley's hot-tempered side is on show with this Anger Deluxe Talking Doll. He's not happy, and he's happy to let you know it. Press his hand to hear 13 phrases, and see his red face light up, plus you can create your own memory ball.

Your tummy will be hot-tempered after sipping from Anger's hefty hot beverage mug. Keep your cool under control from the Inside Out.

Inside Out is a 2015 American 3D computer-animated comedy-drama film produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures. The film is set in the mind of a young girl, Riley Andersen, where five personified emotions—Joy, Sadness, Fear, Anger, and Disgust —try to lead her through life as she moves with her parents to a new city. 

Divertida-Mente é um desenho animado 3D produzido pela Pixar Animation Studios e pela Walt Disney Pictures. O filme é definido na cabeça de uma jovem garota, Riley, onde 5 emoções - Medo, Tristeza, Alegria, Nojinho, Raiva-. tentam levar a menina através de sua vida.

『インサイド・ヘッド』（Inside Out）は、2015年公開のアメリカ合衆国のコンピュータアニメーション3D映画。アメリカ合衆国では2015年6月19日、日本では2015年7月18日に公開された。

Here is what "Inside Out" is called in other languages:  玩轉腦朋友 , 玩转脑朋友 , Vice Versa , ALLES STEHT KOPF

Here's how Toys is called in other languages: juegos, juguetes, giocattoli, spielwaren, brinquedos, carrinhos, spielsachen, leker, spielzeug, jouets, speelgoed, 玩具,leksaker, खिलौने, игрушки, đồ chơi, oyuncaklar, zabawki, bréagáin, Παιχνίδια, トイズ, 장난감, ġugarelli, hračky, іграшки.

Please watch our other videos! Here is our most popular one:
FROZEN MAKEUP BEAUTY KIT FROZEN TOY Disney Princess Elsa Anna Olaf
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CT1Oiwcw3hk

Subscribe to our channel to see videos of the other talking "Inside Out" dolls:  Disgust, Sadness, Joy, and Fear.  Enjoy!!! :-)

snippet.title: Rusty Rivets Rusty Crush Action Figures Spin Master Toy Unboxing || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Rusty and Crush set includes a Rusty figure, Crush figure, and a mini build. All of the pieces and characters work with the Rusty Rivets Build Me Rivet System to design, build, and create unique creations! Collect all of the Rusty Rivets characters, including the Bits, and recreate your favorite builds from the show. If you can dream, you can build it!

Easy build designs make it simple for kids to combine it and design it just like Rusty and Ruby!

Includes Rusty and Crush figures, plus a mini build. Watch the handle spin and articulate treads.

All of the Rusty Rivets Build Me Rivet System sets work together to create unique designs.

The Rusty Rivets Build Me Rivet System is for ages 3+. No batteries required.

Includes: 1 Rusty Figure, 1 Crush Figure, 1 Mini Build

A Rusty Rivets unboxing, demo and review by Keith's Toy Box.

Click here for more Rusty Rivets Toys:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK2Hsmfwd6bECELOHfZvjOII

RUSTY RIVETS Complete Toys from Spin Master Rivet Lab, Botasaur || Keith's Toy Box
https://youtu.be/583gnDKKDE4


Rusty Rivets is a Canadian CGI interactive animated television series produced by Arc Productions and Spin Master Entertainment for Treehouse TV and Nickelodeon Productions. Inspired by elements of the maker culture, it follows the adventures of a young inventor named Rusty and his team of customized robots. A boy named Rusty Rivets uses his knowledge of engineering to repurpose machine parts and create gadgets. He lives in the city of Sparkton Hills along with his friend Ruby Ramirez, a robotic tyrannosaurid named Botasaur, and a group of smaller robots known as the Bits. The show highlights a variety of concepts related to basic science and technology.

Rusty uses the recurring catch phrase "modify, customize, Rustify" when personalizing inventions. Ruby changes the last word to "Rubify" when she does the alterations.


=========================================

snippet.title: Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky High Bridge Jump Fisher-Price -  Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
Watch Thomas complete his most breathtaking stunt yet in the Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky-High Bridge Jump from Fisher-Price. This Thomas & Friends train set breaks new ground by taking Thomas off the tracks and sending him soaring through the air, delivering speed, excitement, and motorized action like only TrackMaster train sets can! Inspired by the Thomas & Friends DVD, The Great Race, Sky-High Bridge Jump brings the movie to life with fast-paced, flying thrills. After a tall, spiral ascent with Harold the helicopter, Thomas speeds down a huge ramp and the velocity launches him into the air! Thomas soars for over two feet (0,6 meters) through the air before landing safely on the other side and continuing his journey. This one-of-a-kind Thomas & Friends train set also features a cargo hopper, waving flags, a barrel cargo piece, and removable Harold the helicopter.
- Complete Thomas & Friends train set includes motorized Thomas train, Harold the helicopter, cargo hopper, cargo piece, and full track layout with ramp and bridge jump
- Send Thomas under the bridge and up the spiral track
- When Thomas reaches the end of the track, Harold will lift him to the top of the ramp
- Thomas lands safely and continues his journey around the rails
- Tip the hopper to drop the barrel onto the tracks and Thomas will push it into the cargo area

Available at Amazon here:
